{"title":"青城山下（四首）","authors":["戈壁舟"],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":5,"day":10}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"青城山下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（四首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"戈壁舟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"清水河"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"六十年前的清水沟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一场大水给冲走！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"清水河泛滥了六十年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们要它变成饱水田。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青城山头戴银盔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开来了开荒突击队。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青城山下在打白头霜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"八十六岁的尚洪顺硬要来开荒。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上河下河人声吼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"清水河又变成清水沟。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"清明"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"往年的清明撒谷子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今年的清明赶栽秧；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"往年栽秧靠男子汉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今年妇女也下秧田；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"往年谷子亩产几百斤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今年要打两千斤！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赵老汉撕掉旧皇历，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"密栽秧子好积极。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"评比台"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十字路口摆擂台，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有本事的都拿出来："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"驾飞机，开火车，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坐不上汽车，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也要骑部自行车，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千百万人抢火箭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁愿去推鸡公车！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生产战场上比身手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英雄跟着人造卫星走！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"号声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红旗卷起启明星，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"田野上飘着洋号声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"个个林盘里哨子响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鸟儿的甜梦被惊醒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"条条小溪条条的路鸟声、人声，锄影、牛影。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}